BEGIN_TEXT
Differentiate \(W = k \sqrt{y + A}\), where \(k\) and \(A\) are constants.
$BR
Answer: \( {dW\over dy} = \) \{ans_rule(55)\}
END_TEXT

ANS(fun_cmp($ans, 'var'=>['A', 'k', 'y'], 'limits'=>[[1,10],[1,10],[1,10]]));

